c=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:48:36.000Z","msg":"其實都幾難<br />\n真係要睇哂佢返計車出車製車 車廠<br />\n散戶好難做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6c55b2219fa920b9d6ae63454204e475742516","tid":1326823,"uid":247972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cef62be8f5f87db252ce5f1c9e3e691c4da7ccd7","tid":1326823,"uid":112161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1da564f3a42014072c42aad258339d3f15fc55f4","tid":1326823,"uid":247972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:41:03.000Z","msg":"What about a particular event"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:49:27.000Z","msg":"Technically it can be validated<br />\nFor example you can anchor your expectation or strategy on whether Trump and Xi can sign a deal"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T23:26:58.000Z","msg":"But how to put that into valuation"},{"pid":"8b450d6fe451ecd883b8c2054bb5a4946cfd3882","tid":1326823,"uid":32859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:52:03.000Z","msg":"講緊我地連登既價值老散 格蛇？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c6afc2bcbb13a31535756603480bab309c87ae","tid":1326823,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:02:29.000Z","msg":"又bin我格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a714237d826bbeeafa4fd339dbdde0fc3117fd85","tid":1326823,"uid":159545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:06:27.000Z","msg":"格 sir 衰太串加唔肯改<br />\n<br />\n強如巴老都會認錯<br />\n<br />\n格 sir 口氣大到話咩睇三千 usd<br />\n<br />\n俾著我咪講比現價有一倍升幅咪算(當時200usd)<br />\n<br />\n同遲遲唔貼倉。貼下 demo 撚下信徒都好"},{"pid":"b045f47b5f8e1338ab0bd17286fc8ecd13b7ee57","tid":1326823,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a714237d826bbeeafa4fd339dbdde0fc3117fd85","tid":1326823,"uid":159545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep